  <brief_title>Postoperative Analgesia With Local Infiltration After Femoral Neck Fracture</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postoperative Analgesia With Local Infiltration After Femoral Neck Fracture vs. Traditional Treatment of Pain With Opioids</official_title>
  <sponsors>
